summary:
- **Announcement Type**: Distribution Update  
- **Key Points**:  
  - Treasury Wine Estates (TWE) appointed Breakthru Beverage Group (BBG) as exclusive distributor in California (replacing RNDC), effective 1 September 2025.  
  - Financial impact of the distributor change remains uncertain; update to be provided with full-year results on 13 August 2025.  
  - No quantified guidance on earnings or operational impact disclosed.
